title: Trevor Noah - Its my culture
description:
[img]http://media2.takealot.com/covers/30051353/culture-full.jpg[/img]

From London to Letterman, Trevor Noah has been through 6 countries since his last wildly successful Thats Racist tour. With all new material his new show 'It's my Culture' takes you with him on his travels from New Zealand to Zambia, New York and London.


'It's My Culture" shines Trevor in a global spotlight without ever forgetting the country where it all started. The craziness of home on the world stage let's everybody know, it's his culture.
